    "body" : "<p><strong>IntelliJ IDEA:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li><p><strong>14</strong> &amp; <strong>15</strong> &amp; <strong>16 EAP</strong></p>\n\n<p><code>File &gt; Settings... &gt; Editor &gt; Code Style &gt; Java &gt; Imports</code> > in <code>General</code> area add a big number for <code>Class count to use import with '*':</code> / <code>Names count to use static import with '*':</code></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/K5WCg.png\" alt=\"File &gt; Settings... &gt; Editor &gt; Code Style &gt; Java &gt; Imports &gt; General &gt; Class count to use import with &#39;*&#39;\"></p></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>IntelliJ IDEA:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li><p><strong>12</strong> &amp; <strong>13</strong></p>\n\n<p><code>File &gt; Settings... &gt; Code Style &gt; Java &gt; Imports</code> > in <code>General</code> area add a big number for <code>Class count to use import with '*':</code>\n<img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/NCdpq.png\" alt=\"File &gt; Settings... &gt; Code Style &gt; Java &gt; Imports &gt; General &gt; Class count to use import with &#39;*&#39;\"></p>\n\n<p>P.S.: <code>Java</code> is after <code>Code Style</code> in the path.</p></li>\n</ul>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
