    "question_id" : 3587071,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>And you also have to remove package names from the \"Packages to use import with *\" list box just below the \"Class count to use import with <em>\" text boxes. Swing and AWT are there by default I think. I still was having import javax.swing.</em>; added even though I had the class count set to 999. I used the minus sign button to remove Swing and Awt from the box and then it worked. </p>\n"
